Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在於子彈的價格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據稱 在卡拉奇近郊的漁港
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法魯多被CIA逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」先前在CIA內部有眼線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已經被處理掉了 就算我們不行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工廠運送「花苞」的車被「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有幸存者 則進行營救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊者可能就是「花苞」本身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們容易被捕就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知故問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道翻花繩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過活動指尖使大腦活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對預防痴呆有一定效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我的表情很嚇人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0095,0000,,UA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs32}「UA」是斯瓦希里語「花」的意思 同時意味著「死」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就是在我心頭盛開的花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱鬧的廟會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 讓我檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是數位的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片要經過精心沖洗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能成為大澤瑪麗亞的眼睛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很有志氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣的攝影師是混不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報導之神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只把機會留給有準備的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 實先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真虧您能得到在這裡設立外資PMC的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs34}（PMC：Private Millitary Contractor 私營軍事承包商）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我事先做足了工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點投資 打一仗就收回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家就簡單在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請務必把資產運作交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 開發部門好像也有些有趣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您知道所謂「聯覺」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視覺 聽覺 味覺 觸覺 嗅覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相互獨立的五感同時作用之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「聯覺者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文字會帶上顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音會化為可見的實體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具體形式因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮能否把它用在敵我識別上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動用五感認知通過視覺得到的情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在動身去迎接姐姐之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先沐浴淨身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有聯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也能通過淨化後的肌膚感知到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低沉的心跳讓我的腹肌震顫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的心跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我體內的「{\1c&H0000FF&\3c&HFF0055&\blur2}紅{\r}」熊熊燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的秘書在洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪 拿華爾街報告來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 沒事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 多謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社長 差不多到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實先生到哪裡去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目不轉睛地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正視這個未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這就是她所見的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我聽不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家一直 一直想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你卻杳無音信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在和壞人戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應當說 是些蠢貨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是我打中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人 想找茬的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這個布娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為它沒有顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在可是廟會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個帶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手背過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣就動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是根線罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一扯就斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要扯斷它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有它 我們才成為朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你使壞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點痴呆的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和精心照顧他的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多麼美好的場面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我找錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想來 這也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 大澤…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好華麗的表演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這可不是鬧著玩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些家伙… 以為這是什麼餘興節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 現實就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們卻故意視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪小姐 是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軟蛋 多用点力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔 唔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！ 迦南？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯 你也在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大澤 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南她 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命 如此絢爛奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至無法直視
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想去碰觸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真死板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小丫頭真是「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」的老大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯恐天下不亂的武裝集團…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是媒體大肆渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混淆了視聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}終究是{\1c&H000000\3c&HFFFFFF\bord2}蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會在地上爬來爬去罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前衛被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是路邊炸彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停車 馬上給我停車！
